<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Herrnstein</ENAMEX> and <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Murray</ENAMEX> begin by telling us that the liberal position on
IQ--namely, "<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Intelligence</ENAMEX> is a bankrupt concept"--has been discredited, and
that "a scholarly consensus has been reached" around their position. This
consensus is "beyond significant technical dispute." Thus, by the end of their
introduction, they have arranged matters so that if intelligence has any
