elite-university <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">student bodies</ENAMEX>. But this is tautological: Any <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">group</ENAMEX> selected
on the basis of scores on mental tests will be composed disproportionately of
<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">people</ENAMEX> who score high on mental tests. Proving <ENAMEX TYPE="WORK_OF_ART">The Bell Curve</ENAMEX> 's thesis
would require proving that success increasingly correlates with IQ in areas of
