database called the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">National Longitudinal Study of Youth</ENAMEX>. The <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">authors</ENAMEX> claim to
demonstrate that high IQ is more predictive of economic success than any other
