assess the merits of the regression analysis. "I am not a <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">scientist</ENAMEX>. I know
nothing about psychometrics," wrote <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Leon Wieseltier</ENAMEX> (who was otherwise quite
critical) in a typical disclaimer.

